  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 49-1-43, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO CLARIFY THAT A CONSERVATION OFFICER MAY PERFORM CERTAIN SEARCHES WITHOUT A WARRANT ONLY WITHIN STATE WILDLIFE MANAGEMENT AREAS OR STATE WILDLIFE REFUGES; TO PROVIDE THAT A CONSERVATION OFFICER MUST HAVE PROBABLE CAUSE AND A WARRANT TO CONDUCT CERTAIN SEARCHES IN AREAS OTHER THAN STATE WILDLIFE MANAGEMENT AREAS OR STATE WILDLIFE REFUGES; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
